data.description: Welcome to 1681 West Siesta Drive. This dynamic home, built in 2021, offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and Colorado charm. Boasting 1972 square feet of living space on a sprawling 1.09-acre lot, this property is ready to accommodate your every need. Step inside to discover a spacious layout featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The open-concept living area is highlighted by an inviting electric fireplace, setting the stage for cozy gatherings or relaxing evenings at home. The kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with stainless steel appliances and plenty of counter space for meal prep. With a convenient island and stylish finishes, it's sure to inspire your culinary creativity. This home is not only stylish but, also eco-friendly, thanks to the addition of solar panels on the roof. Say goodbye to high energy bills and hello to sustainable living! With a generous 3-car garage, there's ample space for parking, storage, or tinkering on projects. Plus, the expansive backyard provides endless opportunities for outdoor fun and relaxation. This property offers the best of both worlds: modern comforts and easy access to everything Pueblo West has to offer. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the vibrant lifestyle awaiting you at 1681 West Siesta Drive!
